@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #fcfcfd
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam arrowColor #0f172a
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #fff7d6
skinparam noteBorderColor #b45309
skinparam noteFontColor #334155
skinparam roundcorner 16
title Shared Reconcile Activity
skinparam activity {
  backgroundColor #f8fafc
  borderColor #0f172a
  fontColor #0f172a
  diamondBackgroundColor #e2e8f0
  diamondBorderColor #1d4ed8
  diamondFontColor #0f172a
  startColor #1d4ed8
  endColor #0f172a
  barColor #1d4ed8
}
start
:Common reconcile flow specialized by\ncontroller-local activity diagrams;
:Step 1. Read desired spec and existing status\nfrom Kubernetes.;
:Step 2. Resolve current OCI identity through\nGET or datasource list fallback before\nchoosing bind, create, update, or delete.;
:Step 3. Apply controller-local spec, secret,\nand delete policies while keeping\nBaseReconciler invariants intact.;
:Step 4. Project OSOK status, finalizer state,\nand retryable conditions back to the\nreconciler.;
stop
legend right
Common reconcile flow specialized by
controller-local activity diagrams
--
Shared Contract (#0F172A)
Shared reconcile semantics and common
controller invariants.
--
Provider Facts (#0F766E)
Imported terraform-provider-oci operations,
waits, datasource behavior, and lifecycle
states.
--
Controller Local (#1D4ED8)
Per-controller specialization derived from
manifest rows and spec settings.
--
Repo Authored (#B45309)
OSOK-only status, finalizer, Secret, and
delete semantics captured in formal specs and
gaps.
endlegend
@enduml
